<subSubSection id="C32D6503FFF8FFF66199444621A56D5C" pageId="4" pageNumber="27" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8B883688FFF8FFF66199444621A56D5C" blockId="4.[151,1127,1050,1169]" pageId="4" pageNumber="27">
<emphasis id="B943EA9AFFF8FFF66199444621636D1C" bold="true" box="[151,280,1050,1073]" pageId="4" pageNumber="27">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species is named after my friend and colleague Svata Bílý on reaching his 70 
<superScript id="7C429BC0FFF8FFF661D44465209D6D6A" attach="left" box="[218,230,1081,1095]" fontSize="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="27">th</superScript>
year, in recognition to all of the excellent work he has produced in adding to our knowledge of the 
<taxonomicName id="4C374D0BFFF8FFF66059440621A16D5C" authorityName="Leach" authorityYear="1815" box="[343,474,1114,1137]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="27" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Buprestidae</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
